div.div:
Downstream permissions are not applied to higher level groups.
E.g. the
"lang:V" permission is not applied to "Private Users". For "Private Users" to gain view access to "Languages", it needs to have "lang:V" permission on "Private Content" to gain the same permission to the child group "Languages".
A better way would have been to give "Private Users" direct "lang:V" access to "Languages", but for the sake of explaining inheritance we applied it via "Private Content"
